  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Retrospective study in the 3 intensive care units of the Brest Teaching Hospital (France)
      during a 18-months period (June 2014 -December 2015) to study the independent association
      between hypophosphatemia and 90-day mortality.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
